i bought this for flight of the Intruder, don't really like having to but other movie that I haven't heard of, but price was right.
Flight of the Intruder is a great movie and story, for a great price we bought it with Extreme Ops and it is NOT!

Been looking for Extreme Opts for a long time and I have told several people about it suggested they watch it. Story was good  and the stunts were outstanding, they did a great job in getting this movie done. was happy to get both great movies together.
